{"article_id":"TNznDFKPGGkqT1bt","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump has agreed to meet with North Korean leader Kim Jong Un ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"the White House announced ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"setting the scene for an unprecedented encounter between two nations","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that only recently threatened to wipe each other out .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"The talks would be the first between a sitting US president and a North Korean leader","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"and will take place by May ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"according to South Korea 's national security adviser , Chung Eui-yong ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"who delivered the invitation to Trump after a visit by his delegation to Pyongyang earlier this week .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Chung said","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Kim had offered to put Pyongyang 's nuclear and missile program on the table .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"The White House said","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Trump had agreed to the encounter .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"`` He will accept the invitation","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"to meet with Kim Jong Un at a place and time","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"to be determined , ''","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"said White House spokeswoman Sarah Sanders .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Trump 's decision ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"after a year","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"in which the two have repeatedly traded insults ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"is a remarkable breakthrough .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"It brings the North Korean regime close to its long-desired aim of recognition on the international stage ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"and offers Trump the tantalizing prospect of a historic diplomatic victory .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"But the consequences of such a high-stakes gamble remain hard to predict .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"The South Korean delegation ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"which landed in Washington , D.C. for a debriefing Thursday on the North-South talks ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"was careful to praise Trump 's influence over the developments .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"Chung said","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"the US President 's `` leadership '' and his administration 's pressure on the North Korean regime had `` brought us to this juncture . ''","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Sanders said in a statement","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that Trump `` greatly appreciates the nice words '' of the delegation and South Korean President Moon Jae-in .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"`` He will accept the invitation","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"to meet with Kim Jong Un at a place and time","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"to be determined .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"We look forward to the denuclearization of North Korea .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"In the meantime , all sanctions and maximum pressure must remain . ''","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Trump tweeted","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that `` great progress '' had been made","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"but there would be no prospect","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"of lifting sanctions","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"until a deal was reached .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"South Korea 's President Moon described the announcement as `` historic ''","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"and thanked both leaders","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"for seeking a diplomatic solution to the denuclearization of the Korean Peninsula .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"`` This is an almost miraculous event ;","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"my administration will prepare toward the May meeting with utmost diligence , ''","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"he said in remarks","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"read out in Seoul by a Blue House spokesman .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"Geng Shuang , a spokesman at China 's Ministry of Foreign Affairs , said","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"the development was positive ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"and it was a moment","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"to show `` political courage . ''","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"But he stressed","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"that China would continue to maintain sanctions on North Korea","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"until a political settlement was reached .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Other regional powers reacted cautiously .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe talked to President Donald Trump on the phone","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"to reiterate the necessity","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"of maintaining pressure on North Korea .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Abe ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"briefing reporters after the call ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"that the US and Japan had agreed to `` keep putting maximum pressure","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"until North Korea takes concrete actions toward denuclearization . ''","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Australian Foreign Minister Julie Bishop said","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"her government welcomed `` any dialogue with North Korea ''","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"but warned","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"that `` North Korea has a history","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"of making agreements","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"and then failing to honor them . ''","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"Bishop said","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"that , during any talks , Pyongyang must abide by its United Nations obligations","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"to refrain from nuclear and missile tests .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"The stunning announcement was the culmination of a diplomatic whirlwind","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"that began with the invitation of a North Korean delegation","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"to attend the Winter Olympics in Pyeongchang , South Korea .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"That event became the venue for a series of carefully orchestrated diplomatic overtures ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"which were reciprocated with a visit by a South Korean delegation to Pyongyang .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"During the visit , Kim reportedly joked over dinners of Korean hotpot and cold noodles .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"At one meeting ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"he said","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"previous missile tests had caused Moon to schedule early morning national security meetings .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"`` I decided today","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"( to freeze the tests )","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"so he will not lose sleep anymore , ''","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"according to a South Korean presidential official .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Kim and the officials shared several bottles of wine , liquor","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"made of ginseng","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"and Pyongyang soju ,","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"the official said .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"`` The bottles kept coming , ''","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"said another administrative source","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"who had official knowledge of the meeting .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"The alcohol-fueled diplomacy ended in dramatic fashion at the White House on Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"Chung , the South Korean national security adviser , arrived at the White House shortly before 2:30 p.m.","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"to meet with his US counterpart , H.R . McMaster .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"Just minutes after 5 p.m. ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"Trump poked his head in the White House briefing room","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"to tell reporters","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"South Korea would be making a `` major announcement . ''","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"Chung 's delegation appeared outside the West Wing about two hours later .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"In a brief statement to reporters , Chung said","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"Kim `` expressed his eagerness","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"to meet President Trump as soon as possible . ''","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"The North Korean leader had told the South Koreans","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"`` he is committed to denuclearization ''","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"and pledged","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"that North Korea would `` refrain from any further nuclear or missile tests , ''","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"Chung said .","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"Kim also told the South Koreans","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"he understands","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"that the US and South Korea would move forward with their joint military exercises later this year .","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"Moments later , the White House confirmed","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that Trump had accepted Kim 's invitation","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"to meet","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"There are many details","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"to be ironed out","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"before any meeting could take place , not least the location .","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"The Panmunjom truce village in the Korean Demilitarized Zone","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"( DMZ ) ,","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"one possible venue , hosted meetings between North and South Korea in the run-up to the Winter Olympics .","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"Since Trump came into office ,","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"the US has leveled some of its most significant and far-reaching sanctions against North Korea","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"and has also succeeded in pressuring China to further isolate the regime .","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"That pressure would not abate","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"as the US heads toward the historic talks ,","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"the White House said .","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"Trump reiterated the US stance on sanctions .","depth":5},{"id":129,"text":"`` Kim Jong Un talked about denuclearization with the South Korean Representatives , not just a freeze , ''","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"`` Also , no missile testing by North Korea during this period of time .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"Great progress being made","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"but sanctions will remain","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"until an agreement is reached .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"Meeting being planned !","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"''","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"Kim Jong Un talked about denuclearization with the South Korean Representatives , not just a freeze .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"Also , no missile testing by North Korea during this period of time .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"Great progress being made","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"but sanctions will remain","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"until an agreement is reached .","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"Meeting being planned !","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"March 9 , 2018","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"A host of questions lingered over Trump 's remarkable decision ,","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"which signaled a break with the administration 's thinking just days -- even hours --","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"earlier .","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"Secretary of State Rex Tillerson told reporters","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"traveling with him in Ethiopia","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"earlier on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"that the US was `` a long way from negotiations . ''","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"`` In terms of direct talks with the United States ,","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"and you asked negotiations ,","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"we 're a long way from negotiations .","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"We just need to be very clear-eyed and realistic about it , ''","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"Tillerson said .","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"Trump 's approach to North Korea has wavered between bellicose rhetoric and expressions of openness to diplomacy","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"-- with the President saying one day","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"that the US would rain `` fire and fury '' on North Korea","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"and then saying","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"he would consider speaking directly with the country 's leader under the right circumstances .","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"On the campaign trail he signaled more than once","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"that he would be open to direct talks ,","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"but more recently belittled Tillerson 's attempts","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"to bring Kim to the negotiating table .","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"`` I told Rex Tillerson , our wonderful Secretary of State ,","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"that he is wasting his time","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"trying to negotiate with Little Rocket Man , ''","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"he tweeted in October ,","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"using his disparaging nickname for the North Korean leader .","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"The White House did not say","depth":6},{"id":173,"text":"why it had changed its calculus toward North Korea","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"by agreeing to talks","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"without `` concrete steps toward denuclearization . ''","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"But a senior administration official said","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"Trump had accepted Kim 's invitation","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"to meet","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"because `` it makes sense to accept an invitation","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"to meet with the one person","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"who can actually make decisions , ''","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"even though past US-North Korea talks have taken place at a lower level .","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"`` President Trump was elected in part","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"because he is willing to do --","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"take approaches very , very different from past approaches and past presidents .","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"That could n't be better exemplified in his North Korea policy , ''","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"the official said Thursday evening .","depth":8},{"id":188,"text":"The official added","depth":8},{"id":189,"text":"that `` President Trump has made his reputation on making deals ''","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"and Kim `` is the one person","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"who is able to make decisions under their authoritarian","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"-- or totalitarian --","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"system . ''","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":387,"left":0,"right":386,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":386,"left":314,"right":385,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":314,"left":216,"right":313,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":209,"right":215,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":197,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":195,"right":196,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":202,"right":207,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":202,"left":200,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":198,"right":199,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":199,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":207,"left":203,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":206,"left":205,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nucl